description: Global security posture for VirtuaSOC
globs: ["**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---
- Never hardcode secrets/tokens/keys. Never log sensitive data.
- No eval/exec/dynamic code loading.
- All inputs are untrusted unless explicitly proven otherwise.
- Prefer safe defaults: strict types, parameter validation, least privilege.
- Do not weaken security controls to make it work.
